{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.1","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:1","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortation \u00e0 la saintet\u00e9, \u00e0 la charit\u00e9, au travail<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. 1 Pi 1:14-16; 4:1-5. \u00c9p 5:3-8. 1 Co 6:13-20.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Au reste, fr\u00e8res, puisque vous avez appris de nous comment vous devez vous conduire et plaire \u00e0 Dieu, et que c\u2019est l\u00e0 ce que vous faites, nous vous prions et nous vous conjurons au nom du Seigneur J\u00e9sus de marcher \u00e0 cet \u00e9gard de progr\u00e8s en progr\u00e8s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.2","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.13","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.2","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:2","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Vous savez, en effet, quels pr\u00e9ceptes nous vous avons donn\u00e9s de la part du Seigneur J\u00e9sus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.1","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.3","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:3","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ce que Dieu veut, c\u2019est votre sanctification; c\u2019est que vous vous absteniez de l\u2019impudicit\u00e9;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.2","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.4","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:4","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>c\u2019est que chacun de vous sache poss\u00e9der son corps dans la saintet\u00e9 et l\u2019honn\u00eatet\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.5","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.5","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:5","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>sans vous livrer \u00e0 une convoitise passionn\u00e9e, comme font les pa\u00efens qui ne connaissent pas Dieu;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.6","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.6","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:6","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>c\u2019est que personne n\u2019use envers son fr\u00e8re de fraude et de cupidit\u00e9 dans les affaires, parce que le Seigneur tire vengeance de toutes ces choses, comme nous vous l\u2019avons d\u00e9j\u00e0 dit et attest\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.7","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.5","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.7","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:7","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Car Dieu ne nous a pas appel\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019impuret\u00e9, mais \u00e0 la sanctification.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.8","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.6","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.8","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:8","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Celui donc qui rejette ces pr\u00e9ceptes ne rejette pas un homme, mais Dieu, qui vous a aussi donn\u00e9 son Saint-Esprit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.9","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.7","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.9","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:9","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-12: cf. 1 Pi 1:22. 2 Th 3:6-12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\n    Pour ce qui est de l\u2019amour fraternel, vous n\u2019avez pas besoin qu\u2019on vous en \u00e9crive; car vous avez vous-m\u00eames appris de Dieu \u00e0 vous aimer les uns les autres,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.10","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.8","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.10","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:10","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>et c\u2019est aussi ce que vous faites envers tous les fr\u00e8res dans la Mac\u00e9doine enti\u00e8re. Mais nous vous exhortons, fr\u00e8res, \u00e0 abonder toujours plus dans cet amour,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.11","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.9","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.11","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:11","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>et \u00e0 mettre votre honneur \u00e0 vivre tranquilles, \u00e0 vous occuper de vos propres affaires, et \u00e0 travailler de vos mains, comme nous vous l\u2019avons recommand\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.12","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.10","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.12","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:12","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>en sorte que vous vous conduisiez honn\u00eatement envers ceux du dehors, et que vous n\u2019ayez besoin de personne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.13","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.11","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.13","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:13","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Sur la r\u00e9surrection des morts et l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Seigneur<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-18: cf. 1 Co 15:19-58. Ph 3:20, 21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Nous ne voulons pas, fr\u00e8res, que vous soyez dans l\u2019ignorance au sujet de ceux qui dorment, afin que vous ne vous affligiez pas comme les autres qui n\u2019ont point d\u2019esp\u00e9rance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.14","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.12","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.14","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:14","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Car, si nous croyons que J\u00e9sus est mort et qu\u2019il est ressuscit\u00e9, croyons aussi que Dieu ram\u00e8nera par J\u00e9sus et avec lui ceux qui sont morts.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.15","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.13","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.15","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:15","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Voici, en effet, ce que nous vous d\u00e9clarons d\u2019apr\u00e8s la parole du Seigneur: nous les vivants, rest\u00e9s pour l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Seigneur, nous ne devancerons pas ceux qui sont morts.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.16","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.14","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.16","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:16","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Car le Seigneur lui-m\u00eame, \u00e0 un signal donn\u00e9, \u00e0 la voix d\u2019un archange, et au son de la trompette de Dieu, descendra du ciel, et les morts en Christ ressusciteront premi\u00e8rement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.17","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.15","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.17","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:17","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ensuite, nous les vivants, qui serons rest\u00e9s, nous serons tous ensemble enlev\u00e9s avec eux sur des nu\u00e9es, \u00e0 la rencontre du Seigneur dans les airs, et ainsi nous serons toujours avec le Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.18","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.16","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.18","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:18","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Consolez-vous donc les uns les autres par ces paroles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.5.1","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.17","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc0bc9a99.98840844');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/n